{"tid":1892767,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】美國公司研發出疫苗 承諾免費贈予疫情嚴重國家","createTime":"2020-02-22T18:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T13:03:29.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"92e5c0694ef274454c0784f3da3d54c0477249a0","tid":1892767,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:03:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200222/H5CEVWTPNRCTCVHF7R7OHJ3DMY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200222%2FH5CEVWTPNRCTCVHF7R7OHJ3DMY%2F&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2Bdgkigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=da97a29b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200222%2FH5CEVWTPNRCTCVHF7R7OHJ3DMY%2F&h=485da0ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200222/H5CEVWTPNRCTCVHF7R7OHJ3DMY/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（北美通訊） 武漢肺炎（COVID-19）蔓延全球，不少國家正在努力研發疫苗對付。美國一間基因工程公司指，已研發出武漢肺炎疫苗，並開始進行動物測試。若然成功，將會免費贈送給受災最嚴重的國家。<br />\n<br />\n記者：李詩敏<br />\n<br />\n位於美國德州的基因工程公司Greffex宣佈，已研發出預防COVID-19的疫苗。公司主席兼行政總裁普賴斯（John Price）表示，科學家是於這星期完成研發，並會將疫苗送交相關政府機構，包括美國的食品及藥物管理局（FDA），以及中國和其他受災嚴重國家的類似監管機構，進行動物測試。<br />\n<br />\n為了安全起見，Greffex並沒有使用活的或已死亡的病毒來製造疫苗，而是使用了腺病毒載體（adenovirus-based vector）疫苗，該疫苗被廣泛用於抵抗各種傳染病或癌症。普賴斯表示，製造疫苗的竅門是能否按照比例生產一定疫苗數量、能否快速和有效測試，並用於患者身上。他又指，如果疫苗獲得政府批准，將免費贈送給受災最嚴重的國家。<br />\n<br />\nGreffex於2019年9月，與美國國家過敏及傳染性疾病研究所（National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases），簽訂了一份價值1,890萬美元合同，研究對抗傳染病，而武漢肺炎疫苗是這次研究的產物。<br />\n<br />\n目前為止，全球感染武漢肺炎已超過7.5萬人，死亡人數達2,100人，當中，中國死亡病例佔大多數。"},{"pid":"03400b6bec032bf6ebc6fde8bb38ecad0c683cd9","tid":1892767,"uid":145190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:24:39.000Z","msg":"測試完D病毒都死撚哂la 咪比支那搵到解藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e83bbf9bc0d94c9201a43100cb0d99008c56818","tid":1892767,"uid":303359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:24:42.000Z","msg":"美帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死力架返去含甴曱平條撚喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4d36ae8c7f9d07bbec5a1588c62fc97242219c","tid":1892767,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:31:13.000Z","msg":"免費白老鼠"},{"pid":"93256cde79099bfaedcd034e6c9f5967adf5817e","tid":1892767,"uid":147071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T19:39:04.000Z","msg":"所以成龍肯捐一百萬未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5651c9280047679bd2a151f2c17b1a28bee283f2","tid":1892767,"uid":275415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T13:03:29.000Z","msg":"按照連登既邏輯<br />\n幫中國等於奶共<br />\n樓主po左係咪得罪連登仔"}]}